How much space does carriers take up?
The data frame in R takes up 2 orders of magnitude of memory more than the table which just points to the object in SQL.

carriers |&gt;
  object.size() |&gt;
  print(units = "Kb")

5.2 Kb

carriers_tibble |&gt;
  object.size() |&gt;
  print(units = "Kb")

234.8 Kb

